'''Loren Lannister''', also known as '''Loren I''', is an unseen character in ''[[Game of Thrones (TV series)|Game of Thrones]]''. He is deceased when the series begins and appears in the [[Complete Guide to Westeros]] and [[Histories &amp; Lore]] featurettes.
